Title: One tropical girl in the world
DateModified: '2018-01-21'
DatePublished: '2018-04-20'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2018/applications/one-tropical-girl-in-the-world
SetInCountry: Ireland
Category: A decision that pushed me to the edge
AuthorName: Fernanda Holanda
AuthorCountry: France
Text: In 2014 Lizzy decided leave her tropical country in Brazil to live in a green
  island over atlantic call Ireland. She left all her confortable zone, her family,
  friend and stable job to start her personal adventure and find more about the world
  and herself. On this adventure she found all the natural's difficulties to start
  a completaly new life in an other country, without speak the new language, without
  know no one else. In fact what she didn't know was that she would find more than
  challenge but also humanity, love, romance, spirituality and a sence to her life.
  Lizza wasn't the same after this time. On her story you will find drama, comedy,
  romance, disagreements and re-encounters and all situation of our every day life,
  from someone who is looking for, have a significant existence in this life. Throught's
  Lizza eyes you will see the world from the view of a tipical tropical girl, full
  of energy, hope and cheer. At the end of her path, Lizza decided keep her travel
  because she believes life is a travel where the only thing we know is it will finish
  soon for it is important be thankful and happy today. I invente you to laught, cry
  even get angry sometimes with Lizza'a story. Share is life. Welcome a board with
  a tropical girl in the world.
